OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1776795065
OL,3,CSeven more arrested over conspiracy to
OL,4,Ccommit arson at another Jewish site
OL,6,FSeven more people have been arrested
OL,7,Ffollowing a series of arson attacks on
OL,8,FJewish sites in London.
OL,10,FThe Metropolitan Police said the
OL,11,Fsuspects were arrested within the past
OL,12,F48 hours over an alleged conspiracy to
OL,13,Fcommit a further arson attack,
OL,14,Falthough the specific target is not
OL,15,Fyet known.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/8
