PN,40402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1776795065
OL,3,CSeven more arrested over conspiracy to
OL,4,Ccommit arson at another Jewish site
OL,6,FSince late March there have been arson
OL,7,Fattacks on Jewish community ambulances
OL,8,Fin Golders Green, two synagogues and a
OL,9,Fformer Jewish charity, as well as an
OL,10,Fincident where a drone was flown near
OL,11,Fthe Israeli embassy.
OL,13,FThe latest arrests by detectives from
OL,14,FCounter-Terrorism Policing London, saw
OL,15,Fthree men aged 24, 25 and 26 held in
OL,16,FHarpenden on Sunday, and on Monday a
OL,17,F25-year-old man arrested in Stevenage,
OL,18,Fas well as a 26-year-old man and two
OL,19,Fwomen aged 50 and 59 detained in a car
OL,20,Fnear Birmingham.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
