CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1776795065
OL,3,CSeven more arrested over conspiracy to
OL,4,Ccommit arson at another Jewish site
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FThe men arrested in Harpenden have
OL,12,Fbeen released on bail, while the other
OL,13,Ffour remain in custody, the
OL,14,FMetropolitan Police said.
OL,16,FAnother arrest has also been made over
OL,17,Fthe embassy incident, that saw a drone
OL,18,Fflown in Kensington Gardens carrying
OL,19,Fjars that were later found to contain
OL,20,Fnon-hazardous material.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/8
