PN,40404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1776795065
OL,3,CSeven more arrested over conspiracy to
OL,4,Ccommit arson at another Jewish site
OL,6,FA 39-year-old man was held in Ealing
OL,7,Funder section 41 of the Terrorism Act,
OL,8,Fwhich allows a suspect to be arrested
OL,9,Fwithout a warrant if they are
OL,10,Fsuspected of being a terrorist.
OL,12,FSo far, 23 people have been arrested
OL,13,Fover the series of attacks on Jewish
OL,14,Fsites.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
