PN,40405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1776795065
OL,3,CSeven more arrested over conspiracy to
OL,4,Ccommit arson at another Jewish site
OL,6,FDeputy Assistant Commissioner Vicki
OL,7,FEvans, the Senior National Co-
OL,8,Fordinator of Counter Terrorism
OL,9,FPolicing, said: "We've made very clear
OL,10,Fthat we will be relentless in our
OL,11,Fpursuit of anyone involved in carrying
OL,12,Fout or planning these arson attacks.
OL,14,F"Our message is clear, we will not
OL,15,Ftolerate this intimidation of our
OL,16,Fcommunities, and will pursue those
OL,17,Fresponsible. One of our key lines of
OL,18,Finquiry is whether criminal proxies `
OL,19,Fthat is to say people being paid money
OL,20,Fto carry out a crime, are being used
OL,21,Fto commit any of these arsons.
OL,26,@qD@QOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
