OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1776795065
OL,3,CSeven more arrested over conspiracy to
OL,4,Ccommit arson at another Jewish site
OL,6,F"While our investigations into this
OL,7,Fare still ongoing, my message to
OL,8,Fanyone even considering getting
OL,9,Finvolved in this type of activity is
OL,10,Fthis, the stakes are high and it is
OL,11,Fabsolutely not worth the risk.
OL,13,F"When we identify you, we will seek to
OL,14,Fprosecute you. This will include
OL,15,Fconsidering offences under the
OL,16,FNational Security Act which comes with
OL,17,Fa significant sentence and lifetime
OL,18,Frestrictions.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
