OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1776795065
OL,3,CSeven more arrested over conspiracy to
OL,4,Ccommit arson at another Jewish site
OL,6,F"We will not rest until all those
OL,7,Fresponsible for these acts are held to
OL,8,Ffull account.
OL,10,F"As well as making arrests, Counter
OL,11,FTerrorism Policing resources have also
OL,12,Fbeen deployed in north-west London to
OL,13,Fsupport the significant Met Police
OL,14,Foperation to help deter further
OL,15,Fattacks and provide reassurance to
OL,16,FJewish places of worship and
OL,17,Fbusinesses.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/8
